column5: Did a little steelhead fishing a trib off of Lake Ontario.  Got into a few fish drifting.
Is there much of an ice shelf to deal with? Nice fish!
Good grief is that milt I see.  I haven't even finished with ice fishing!  How is the shore ice? Looks like a great day.
no the ice wasn't too bad at all.  going to try again this week.  lost a few fish too.
Nice Fish looks like a good day out.
looks like the fish were as excited to see you as you see to see them  hoping to take the boy out a day or 2 next week, hopefully the river clears a little
